[center][IMG]http://aycu33.webshots.com/image/24592/2000816110489262354_rs.jpg[/img][/center][center][b]Welcome to The Real World [/b] [/center]
[center][size=20pt]Remember to sign up for the [url=http://therealworld.smfforfree3.com/][u]Forums[/u]![/size][/center]
[b][size=10pt]Since u prob have heard of this new project by me , im posting some new information about the server.
Before i tell u , i have some bad news also .....
I have had 5 hosters they all left me , idk why ... but that doesnt matter , ill just get a new 1 :)
Information about the server :
Things on the server :
Full range : Wich meens
correct arrow drops Projectile's Max hit is like 90% to rs Hits are based of The Armour + ranged lvl + bonus u have
Full Mage : Wich meens
Correct spells Req. Runes + lvls Projectiles If u use air strike without the runes u will hit 0 .... and nothing else Max hit is like 90% to rs Hits are based of The Armour + mage lvl + bonus u have
95% Melee : Wich meens
Correct speeds Correct hits Max hit is like 90% to rs Hits are based of The Armour + Strengh,attack lvl + bonus u have The Better the armour u wear how harder it is to get hit high
MONEY MAKING
The first time u log on u will start wit a Iron pick in ur hand , U go to North-East. When u are there go mine some Essence to make urself some money .
Price of ess each : 3k Each
Other things u can do is go runecraft and sell the runes , Price have to be picked
TRAINING
Go into the portal and train away
*NOTE* = bring food , cuz if u die u do lose ur stuff :)
SKILLS
Full combat Exept prayer(later)
Mining = essence only (later other)
Woodcutting = 60%
Fletching = Should work
Rune Crafting = COMING SOON
Well this is it for now , more information later , ill post some pics under this[/size][/b]
[b]Brand New starting Point !! Oo !! How Nice!![/b]
[URL=http://allyoucanupload.webshots.com/v/2004779431967575793][IMG]http://aycu08.webshots.com/image/22807/2004779431967575793_rs.jpg[/img][/URL]
[b]Explenation About the portals!![/b]
[URL=http://allyoucanupload.webshots.com/v/2004738347783319676][IMG]http://aycu14.webshots.com/image/22813/2004738347783319676_rs.jpg[/img][/URL]
[b]Real Working Range Projectile!![/b]
[URL=http://allyoucanupload.webshots.com/v/2003490349427819020][IMG]http://aycu28.webshots.com/image/25267/2003490349427819020_rs.jpg[/img][/URL]
Thnx for reading , and i hope ur interested to play on this server :)
See you guys around :rolleyes:
